Mutual Funds Snapshot







Mawer is pleased to offer 13 mutual funds that meet a wide variety of investment needs and risk profiles. Our funds offer no-load investing—no sales or trailing commissions, no set-up fees, and no purchase, transfer or redemption fees. Our Management Expense Ratios (MERs) are among the lowest in Canada. To view a detailed fund profile, select the fund name below. Performance (Net) as at June 30, 2017*
