Mawer Investment Management Limited: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 12:08 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Mawer Investment Management Limited



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mawer Investment Management Limited is an employee owned investment management firm. The firm also provides investment advisory services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to individuals. The firm also caters to high net worth individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, insurance companies, and separately managed accounts. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm also invests in money ...
Mawer Investment Management Limited is an employee owned investment management firm. The firm also provides investment advisory services to its clients. It primarily provides its services to individuals. The firm also caters to high net worth individuals, pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, corporations, insurance companies, and separately managed accounts. It manages separate client-focused equity, fixed income, and balanced portfolios. The firm also launches and manages equity, fixed income, and balanced mutual funds for its clients. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm also invests in money markets. For the equity portion of its portfolio, it primarily invests in growth-oriented value stocks of large-cap and small-cap companies. For the fixed income portion of its portfolio, the firm invests in fixed income securities including Canadian bonds, government treasury bills, debentures of Canadian government and corporate issuers, short-term fixed income securities. It employs a fundamental analysis along with a bottom-up stock selection approach in order to make its investments. The firm benchmarks the performance of its portfolios against the DEX Universe Bond Index, S&P/TSX Composite Index, S&P 500 Index, MSCI EAFE Index, Russell Global Small Cap Index, BMO Nesbitt Burns Small Cap Index, and MSCI World Index. It conducts in-house research while creating its portfolios. Mawer Investment Management Limited was founded in 1974 and is based in Calgary, Canada with an additional office in Toronto, Canada.
Detailed Description


517 - 10th Avenue South WestSuite 600Calgary, AB T2R 0A8CanadaFounded in 1974



Phone: 403-262-4673

Fax: 403-262-4099

